thread.title_full: Auto Europe Canada reviewed by JKH.

author: JKH.
title: JKH.
text: Probably put over 10,000 miles on Auto Europe booked cars over the 10 years I've rented through them on my EU trips. Never a problem yet with reservations, pickup, drop off or car performance. Always fast responses to any queries I may have. I don't even check anyone else's prices anymore as they have in the past always beaten the competition.
